Notes on provenance & ethics: anchor citations here are intentionally public and tamper‑evident; the gate prevents incoherent or non‑consensual data from entering the fossil ledger (Ethics: “No entropy, no entry”). External claims are bound to stable standards (RFC/NIST) with explicit citations for audit.
